<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbd7d3fcf-47c4-11f1-bea6-82cea744851c" identifier="/us/usc/t31/s6207"><num value="6207">§ 6207.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to carry out this chapter such sums as may be necessary for each of the fiscal years 1986, 1987, 1988, 1989, and 1990.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbd7d3fd0-47c4-11f1-bea6-82cea744851c">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/99/547/s2/a">Pub. L. 99–547, § 2(a)</ref>, <date date="1986-10-27">Oct. 27, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/3060">100 Stat. 3060</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
